ts|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=July 12, 2018|work=Billboard|accessdate=July 22, 2018}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Release history==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n| rowspan=\"2\"| February 2, 2018\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| {{hlist|[[Top Dawg Entertainment|Top Dawg]]|[[Aftermath Entertainment|Aftermath]]|[[Interscope Records|Interscope]]}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/black-panther-the-album-music-from-and-inspired-by/1331258584|title=Pray for Me|website=[[iTunes Store]]|accessdate=February 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United Kingdom\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Rhythmic contemporary]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| {{hlist|Top Dawg|[[XO (record label)|XO]]|[[Republic Records|Republic]]|Interscope}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/1xtra/playlist|title=BBC \u2013 Radio 1Xtra \u2013 Playlist|publisher=[[BBC Radio 1]]. [[British Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=February 9, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203174904/http://www.bbc.co.uk/1xtra/playlist|archivedate=February 3, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| United States\n| rowspan=\"2\"| February 6, 2018\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-rhythmic/future-releases|title=Top 40 Rhythmic Future Releases|publisher=All Access|accessdate=February 3, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202212916/https://www.allaccess.com/top40-rhythmic/future-releases|archivedate=February 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases|title=Top 40/M Future Releases|publisher=All Access|accessdate=February 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206082712/https