uildofmusicsupervisors.com/single-post/2019/01/10/GUILD-OF-MUSIC-SUPERVISORS-ANNOUNCES-NOMINEES-FOR-9th-ANNUAL-GMS-AWARDS-SET-FOR-FEBRUARY-13-IN-LOS-ANGELES|title=NOMINEES FOR 9th ANNUAL GMS AWARDS ANNOUNCED|date=January 13, 2019 |access-date=January 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|Best Song/Recording Created for a Film\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2| NAACP Image Award \n| Outstanding Duo, Group or Collaboration\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Music Video/Visual Album \n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n|[[PLAY - Portuguese Music Awards]]\n|[[PLAY - Portuguese Music Awards#Best International Song|Best International Song]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from digital booklet.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://genius.com/Various-artists-black-panther-the-album-booklet-lyrics|title=Various Artists \u2013 Black Panther: The Album [Booklet]|website=[[Genius (website)|Genius]]|accessdate=February 9, 2018|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6x6jb9RKo?url=https://genius.com/Various-artists-black-panther-the-album-booklet-lyrics|archive-date=2018-02-09|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n'''Performers'''\n* [[Kendrick Lamar]] \u2013 vocals\n* [[SZA (singer)|SZA]] \u2013 vocals\n\n'''Technical'''\n* Matt Schaeffer \u2013 record engineering, mix engineering\n* [[Mike Bozzi]] \u2013 master engineering\n* Sam Ricci \u2013 record engineering\n* James Hunt \u2013 record engineering\n* Lorenzo Richards - record engineering\n\n'''Production'''\n* [[Sounwave]] \u2013 production\n* [[Al Shux]] \u2013 production\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2018)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n{{single chart|Australia|2|artist=Kendrick Lamar & SZA|song=All the Stars|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 24, 2018}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|25|artist=Kendrick Lamar & SZA|song=All the Stars|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 28, 2018}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|21|artist=